   a heal-over-time (HOT) effect and an AC bonus for several rounds. This
   represents the Monk tradition's contribution to the Martial Artist
   synthesis -- making Brawler ferocity sustainable through disciplined
   internal energy management.

   Chi cost: 8 (doubled to 16 if on cooldown via chi_skill_cost)
   Cooldown: 15 rounds
   Duration: 2 + (Martial Artist level / 5) rounds
   HOT modifier: Monk level + Brawler level + (Martial Artist level * 3)
   AC modifier: -(Martial Artist level * 5 + Monk level * 2)

   Distinct from Chakra (burst heal + damroll) and Iron Skin (passive, no
   chi cost). Breath of Endurance is sustained recovery + damage mitigation.
